snippet.title: Best VGM 764 - Dragon Quest III - Dungeon
snippet.description:
Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u4mU3HuESI0

See also:
Best VGM 644 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z41vcQERnQQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES / SNES
Dragon Quest III (1996)
Dungeon
Koichi Sugiyama
